data.description: Welcome to Vinings Run, a condo complex that is in a prime location. This ground level, 1 bed, 1 bath condo is one of the bigger 1 bedroom units in the neighborhood. The location of the 400 building sits on a beautiful courtyard that you can walk out to from your front door also positioned in between the option of the 2 pools for the complex. This unit has plenty of space with an oversized primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and an additional closet for storage. The living room has a fireplace that opens up to the dining room. The best part about this condo is the large walk out patio! You can get to the Battery/Truist Park in minutes as well as plenty of shopping, restaurants and entertainment. This unit is being sold AS-IS. This is a great opportunity to make this condo your own.
